2.caption: 1957 East–West Pro Bowl
2.description: The 1957 Pro Bowl was the NFL's seventh annual all-star game which featured the outstanding performers from the 1956 season. The game was played on January 13, 1957, at the Los Angeles Memorial Coliseum in Los Angeles, California in front of 44,177 fans. The West squad defeated the East by a score of 19–10.
2.inspected:Co-MVPs: Bert Rechichar (Baltimore Colts), Ernie Stautner (Pittsburgh Steelers)
